    A class to be extended by search engine classes that scrape search results from HTML pages. This class provides multiple methods for common scraping actions shared by all engines, but expects its children to implement specific ways to scrape individual search results. For an example of a class that extends this abstract class, see CorsaroNero and LeetX.
